Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.http

Enum HTTPStatus

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<HTTPStatus>
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.http.HTTPStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<HTTPStatus>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum HTTPStatus extends Enum<HTTPStatus>
Symbolic enumeration of HTTP status codes.

This enum encourages using symbolic values rather than numeric codes, providing type-safe status handling and convenient category-checking methods.

In addition to standard HTTP status codes, this enum includes client-side pseudo-statuses for conditions detected by the client (e.g., redirect loops).

Author:
Chris Burdess
